    <note type="biography">
        <p>Russian administrator. Son of General Stepan Vasil’evich Perfil’ev. Married Praskov’ja Fëdorovna Tolstaya. Governor of Moscow, 1878–87. The prototype of Stiva Oblonskij in Leo Tolstoy’s <hi rend="italic">Anna Karenina.</hi></p></note>
